      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software must be validated under a formal quality management system with documented test suite coverage and version control traceable to CFD solver release used in predictions.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v8) has a documented test suite but lacks ISO 9001 certification and full traceability of hemolysis sub-model validation. Achieved level 2 reflects partial documentation only."
