      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must be conducted at operating conditions matching VAD deployment envelope including hematocrit, temperature, and rotational speed ranges.",
      "rationale": "Available experimental data collected at 37% hematocrit and 25°C rather than physiological 37°C. Rotational speed range partially overlaps VAD envelope. Achieved level 2 due to significant test condition mismatch."
