      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation QoIs must directly correspond to the clinical decision QoI (absolute NIH) rather than surrogate or intermediate quantities.",
      "rationale": "NIH is directly validated as the primary QoI. Velocity field comparisons serve as supporting evidence. Some reliance on intermediate scalar stress proxy rather than direct cell-level hemolysis integration reduces achieved level to 3."
