      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be performed on a geometry and operating regime representative of the target VAD device and patient population, not solely on generic FDA benchmark geometry.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed exclusively on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry. Target VAD geometry differs in impeller blade count and volute design. Geometric dissimilarity limits relevance. Achieved level 2."
