      "rationale": "No independent review of CFD setup or post-processing conducted. Single analyst team performed all simulation and analysis steps. Epistemic gap identified. Achieved level 1."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
