      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form uncertainty for turbulence closure and hemolysis constitutive model must be quantified through comparison of multiple model forms against experimental data.",
      "rationale": "Single turbulence model (SST k-omega) and single hemolysis power-law model used without comparison to alternative formulations. Model form uncertainty unquantified. Critical epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1."
    },
